!Usage notes

The root [[kause]] expresses regret or an apology. It can be used on its own (e.g., «[[Kause!|kause]]» for "Sorry!"), or used like other emotion roots (e.g. «[[I|i]] [[kemi]][[n]] ([[pau]]) [[kause]] [[tete]][[n]] ...»  for "I'm (very) sorry about ... / I apologize (greatly) for ...").